00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:37.000
And that's when some nurses,

00:14:37.000 --> 00:14:41.000
someone said, say, I think she's got a physical problem.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:44.000
And that's when they discovered it.

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:49.000
And that's when they operated to remove her tumor.

00:14:49.000 --> 00:14:53.000
You know, they get down to some tasks from what happened.

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:55.000
But it was too late.

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:59.000
Well, they blew the operand.

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:04.000
Another doctor I'd like to get my hands off.

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:08.000
Yeah, they took the tumor out,

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:11.000
but didn't replace it with anything.

00:15:11.000 --> 00:15:14.000
And half an hour after the operation,

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:17.000
the walls of a brain collapse since he died.

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:20.000
So I had a phone call asking for authority

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:23.000
since I was the young woman of Ken

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:26.000
